(12, '“Siksa Kubur”, Film Terbaru Karya Sutradara Joko Anwar yang Mengisyaratkan Betapa Mengerikannya Siksa Kubur', 5, '&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;JAKARTA,\r\nintelmedianews.com &ndash; &ldquo;Siksa Kubur&rdquo; merupakan film terbaru karya sutradara Joko\r\nAnwar. Sebelumnya, Joko Anwar merilis poster film terbarunya yang berjudul &ldquo;Siksa\r\nKubur&rdquo; pada Senin, 29 Januari 2024.&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Dalam\r\nposter tersebut, terlihat sebuah kuburan yang mulai ditinggalkan oleh para\r\npelayatnya, di tepi liang kuburan terdapat tulisan mengingatkan akan siksa\r\nkubur.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-spacing: 2.1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;\r\nletter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&ldquo;Siapapun\r\nkamu di dunia, tujuh langkah pengantar meninggalkanmu kamu harus bisa menjawab\r\npertanyaan malaikat kubur. Jika gagal, akan datang kepadamu &lsquo;Siksa Kubur&rsquo;,&rdquo;\r\ntampak tulisan di poster itu.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Joko\r\nAnwar juga menuliskan peringatan akan datangnya siksaan di alam kubur kepada\r\nsiapa pun terlepas dari apa yang dikerjakan.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-spacing: 2.1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;\r\nletter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Apapun\r\nyang kita lakukan sekarang: belajar, bekerja, berjualan, berkampanye, menipu\r\nrakyat, korupsi, semua itu bisa jadi hal terakhir yang kita lakukan. Karena\r\nmungkin saja, kita akan tiba-tiba bangun dan sadar sudah ada di bawah\r\nsana,&quot; tulisnya.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-spacing: 2.1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;\r\nletter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Penulis\r\ndan sutradara film &quot;Pengabdi Setan&quot; ini mengumumkan film &quot;Siksa\r\nKubur&quot; akan tayang segera di bioskop.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Film\r\n&ldquo;Siksa Kubur&rdquo; berasal dari film pendek&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Grave Torture&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;garapan Joko\r\nAnwar yang rilis di YouTube pada 2012 lalu. Film layar lebar yang akan tayang\r\nnanti kabarnya akan memiliki keterkaitan dengan film&amp;nbsp;pendeknya ini.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&ldquo;Cerita\r\ndi film Panjang &lsquo;Siksa Kubur&rsquo; akan berkaitan dengan cerita film pendeknya, dan\r\nakan diperluas plot maupun karakternya,&rdquo; kata Joko Anwar&amp;nbsp;melalui\r\nketerangan pers beberapa waktu lalu.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-spacing: 2.1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;\r\nletter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Film\r\npendek itu mengisahkan seorang anak laki-laki yang terjebak dalam peti mati\r\nayahnya.&amp;nbsp;Dengan hanya bermodalkan korek api, anak tersebut harus\r\nmenyaksikan ayahnya disiksa di dalam kubur atas apa yang pernah dilakukannya di\r\ndunia.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Lewat\r\nposter teaser pertamanya, terlihat sejumlah pelayat tampak meninggalkan kuburan\r\ntempat jenazah bersemayam di dalamnya.&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Dalam\r\nposter itu tertulis, &ldquo;Siapa pun kamu di dunia, tujuh langkah pengantar\r\nmeninggalkanmu, kamu harus bisa menjawab pertanyaan Malaikat Kubur. Jika gagal,\r\nakan datang kepadamu: Siksa Kubur.&rdquo;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-spacing: 2.1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;\r\nletter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Poster\r\nteaser tersebut mengisyaratkan betapa mengerikannya siksa yang akan dialami\r\nmanusia tak beriman.&amp;nbsp;Film ini dijanjikan akan memiliki cerita, karakter,\r\ndan isu yang dekat dengan penonton, serta visual yang realistik sampai bikin\r\nterlihat nyata.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt&quot;&gt;Film\r\n&ldquo;Siksa Kubur&rdquo; juga melibatkan para sineas berpengalaman, yakni Tia Hasibuan\r\nsebagai produser, Jaisal Tanjung sebagai sinematografer, dan Allan Sebastian\r\nsebagai direktur seni.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID&quot;&gt;Daftar Pemain Siksa Kubur&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;mso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\ncolor:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Heebo;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;color:#222222;letter-spacing:.15pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID&quot;&gt;Reza Rahadian, Christine\r\nHakim, Slamet Rahardjo, Fachri Albar, Arswendy Bening Swara, Faradina Mufti, Happy\r\nSalma, Jajang C. Noer, Putri Ayudya, Niniek L. Karim, Djenar Maesa Ayu, Muzakki\r\nRamdhan, Widuri Putri, Runny Rudiyanti, Kania Atmaja. (Red)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/banners/magazine-12.png?v=1706625973', 'uploads/pdf/magazine-.pdf?v=1706625973', 1, 1, '2024-01-30 14:46:13', '2024-01-30 14:46:13'),
(13, 'Yenny Wahid Ungkap Kesamaan Kubu 01 dan 03', 3, '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;JAKARTA,\r\nintelmedianews.com - Dewan Pengarah Tim Pemenangan Nasional (TPN)\r\nGanjar-Mahfud, Yenny Wahid, menyambut baik Gerakan Salam 4 Jari yang belakangan\r\nmuncul di media sosial X (dulu Twitter). &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Sebagai\r\ninformasi, Gerakan Salam 4 Jari mendorong agar masyarakat tidak memilih\r\npasangan calon (paslon) presiden dan wakil presiden nomor urut 2 Prabowo\r\nSubianto - Gibran Rakabuming. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Gerakan ini\r\njuga meminta agar paslon 01 Anies Baswedan - Muhaimin Iskandar dan paslon 03\r\nGanjar Pranowo - Mahfud MD bersatu untuk mencegah Prabowo-Gibran memenangkan\r\nPilpres 2024. Yenny pun merasa Gerakan Salam 4 Jari muncul secara alami.\r\nMenurutnya, kini banyak kesamaan antara kubu 01 dan 03.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&quot;Secara\r\nalami pendukung dua paslon ini punya titik-titik kesamaan, sama-sama ingin\r\nberjuang bagi demokrasi, sama-sama gelisah dengan ada banyak sekali potensi\r\nkecurangan yang terjadi, kita tentu concern, kita khawatir kalau ada\r\nupaya-upaya intimidasi,&quot; jelas Yenny di kawasan Stadion GBK Senayan,\r\nJakarta Pusat, dikutip Selasa (30/1/2024).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Dia pun bingung\r\nkarena kubu 02 kerap menarasikan agar Pilpres 2024 berlangsung satu putaran\r\ndengan argumen agar anggaran negara bisa dihemat. Yenny merasa cara berpihak\r\nyang mementingkan anggaran daripada legitimasi kepemimpinan sangat salah. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Putri dari\r\npresiden ke-4 Abdurahman Wahid alias Gus Dur ini berpendapat jika Pilpres 2024\r\nberlangsung satu putaran tapi diduga kecurangan terjadi di mana-mana maka tidak\r\nada legitimasi untuk presiden-wakil presiden yang terpilih.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#1A1A1A&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&quot;Lebih\r\nbaik dua putaran, tapi punya legitimasi kuat di masyarakat sehingga pemimpin\r\nyang dihasilkan dari proses pemilu nantinya itu adalah pemimpin yang sah, yang\r\nbenar-benar dipilih masyarakat,&quot; ujar Yenny. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Lebih lanjut,\r\ndia memastikan komunikasi politik antara 03 dan 01 selalu terjalin karena\r\ndiyakini Pilpres 2024 berlangsung dua putaran. Meski demikian, menurutnya,\r\nbelum ada pembicaraan formal antara tokoh-tokoh utama. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; line-height: 125%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Yenny juga mengakui PDI Perjuangan (PDIP) yang\r\nmendukung 03 dengan Partai Keadilan Sejahtera (PKS) yang mendukung 01 punya\r\nbasis ideologi yang berbeda. Namun, dia menekankan dalam politik yang dicari\r\nadalah persamaan bukan perbedaan.&lt;/span&gt; (Red)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/banners/magazine-13.png?v=1706677524', 'uploads/pdf/magazine-.pdf?v=1706677524', 1, 1, '2024-01-31 05:05:23', '2024-01-31 05:05:24');

